processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Minimal processing. Records remain in original file folders and record storage boxes.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The Christian de Duve papers are comprised of: workshop, conference, symposium, and meeting records; lecture files; administrative files; correspondence; reprints, papers, dissertations, manuscripts, and other publications.
